songs.title: The 11th Hour
songs.lyrics:
I search the world to find the girl
I need, I need
I know she's also searching out
For me, for me

I keep on going way past the 11th hour
I keep on going way past the 11th hour
To find you

I keep on going way past the 11th hour
I keep on going way past the 11th hour
To find you

I search the world to find the girl
I need, I need
I know she's also searching out
For me, for me

I keep on going way past the 11th hour
I keep on going way past the 11th hour

To find you

I keep on going way past the 11th hour
I keep on going way past the 11th hour
To find you

I will...

I keep on going way past the 11th hour
I keep on going way past the 11th hour
To find you

I keep on going way past the 11th hour
I keep on going way past the 11th hour
To find you

I will...
